## Phase 9: End-to-End Testing (Week 5-6)

### 9.1 Critical User Flows

**Create E2E test file:** `tests/e2e/critical-flows.spec.ts`

```typescript
import { test, expect } from '@playwright/test';

test('Complete trading flow', async ({ page }) => {
  // 1. Sign up
  await page.goto('http://localhost:3000/register');
  await page.fill('[name="email"]', 'test@example.com');
  await page.fill('[name="password"]', 'SecurePass123!');
  await page.click('button:has-text("Sign Up")');
  
  // 2.  Deposit funds
  await page.click('text=Wallet');
  await page.click('text=Deposit');
  await page.fill('[name="amount"]', '100');
  await page.fill('[name="cardNumber"]', '4242424242424242');
  await page.fill('[name="expiry"]', '12/25');
  await page.fill('[name="cvc"]', '123');
  await page.click('button:has-text("Deposit")');
  await expect(page.locator('text=Balance: $100')).toBeVisible();
  
  // 3. Create bot
  await page.click('text=Bots');
  await page.click('text=Create Bot');
  await page.fill('[name="name"]', 'Test Bot');
  await page.selectOption('[name="strategy"]', 'ma_crossover');
  await page.fill('[name="amount"]', '50');
  await page.click('button:has-text("Create")');
  
  // 4. Start bot
  await page. click('button:has-text("Start")');
  await expect(page.locator('text=Status: Running')).toBeVisible();
  
  // 5.  Monitor trade
  await page.click('text=Trades');
  await expect(page.locator('. trade-row')).toBeVisible({ timeout: 30000 });
  
  // 6. Stop bot
  await page.click('text=Bots');
  await page. click('button:has-text("Stop")');
  await expect(page.locator('text=Status: Stopped')).toBeVisible();
});
```

**Run E2E Tests:**
```bash
npm run test:e2e
```

### 9.2 Edge Cases & Error Scenarios

**Network Failures:**
